trans-unit.source: Provides a common base implementation for writers of out-going request parameters for Web service clients implemented using HTTP but without SOAP.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en felles basistabellen implementering for forfattere av gamle gå forespørselsparametere for Web service-klienter implementert ved hjelp av HTTP, men uten SOAP.

trans-unit.source: MimeParameterWriter and other classes in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols> namespace support the .NET Framework's implementations of Web services via the HTTP-GET and HTTP-POST operations.
trans-unit.target: MimeParameterWriter og andre klasser i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>navneområdet støtter .NET Framework-implementeringer av webtjenester via HTTP-GET og HTTP-POST-operasjoner.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers serialize and deserialize, respectively, between the parameters or return objects of Web methods and the HTTP request or response streams.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere lesere serialisere og deserialisere henholdsvis mellom parameterne eller return objekter av Web-metoder og HTTP-forespørselen eller svar dataflytene.

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers use HTTP for transport but don't exchange messages using the SOAP standard.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere og lesere bruke HTTP til transport, men exchange ikke meldinger ved hjelp av SOAP-standard.

trans-unit.source: The MimeParameterWriter class establishes a common request-writing format for client-side writing of Web method parameters into HTTP request streams.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MimeParameterWriter oppretter et vanlig forespørselen skriving-format for klientsiden skriving av parameterne for Web-metoden i HTTP-forespørselen dataflyter.

trans-unit.source: You will typically not need to use MimeParameterWriter or its descendant classes directly.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger ikke vanligvis bruker MimeParameterWriter eller de underordnede klassene direkte.

trans-unit.source: Instead, when the Wsdl.exe tool generates client proxy code according to the HTTP-GET or HTTP-POST implementations, it applies the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute> to each Web method and sets the attribute's <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ParameterFormatter%2A> property to the appropriate type.
trans-unit.target: I stedet når verktøyet Wsdl.exe genererer proxy-Klientkoden i henhold til implementeringer HTTP-GET eller HTTP-POST, brukes den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute>til hver Web-metoden og angir attributtets <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ParameterFormatter%2A>egenskapen riktig type.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute.ParameterFormatter%2A> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HttpMethodAttribute>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, modifies the outgoing HTTP request's Uniform Request Locator (URL).
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, endrer du utgående HTTP-forespørselens Uniform forespørselen Locator (URL).

trans-unit.source: Of the classes derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>, only <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.UrlParameterWriter> modifies the HTTP request URL.
trans-unit.target: For klasser som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>, bare <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.UrlParameterWriter>endrer HTTP forespørsels-URL.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.UrlParameterWriter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>

trans-unit.source: The HTTP request's original Uniform Resource Locator (URL).
trans-unit.target: HTTP-forespørselen opprinnelige Uniform Resource Locator (URL).

trans-unit.source: The Web method parameter values to be added to the URL, if necessary.
trans-unit.target: Web-metoden parameterverdier som skal legges til URL-adressen, hvis nødvendig.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> object that contains the modified, outgoing HTTP request's Uniform Request Locator (URL).
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>objekt som inneholder den endrede, Utgående HTTP-forespørsler Uniform forespørselen Locator (URL).</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, initializes the out-going HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, initialiserer den gamle gå HTTP-forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: Of the classes derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>, only <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter> implements the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter> method.
trans-unit.target: For klasser som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>, bare <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter>implementerer den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>metoden.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>

trans-unit.source: The out-going request, where the <xref:System.Net.WebRequest> class allows transport protocols besides HTTP.
trans-unit.target: Gamle gå forespørselen, der den <xref:System.Net.WebRequest>klassen tillater transport protokoller i tillegg til HTTP.</xref:System.Net.WebRequest>

trans-unit.source: The Web method parameter values.
trans-unit.target: Parameterverdiene Web-metoden.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the encoding used to write parameters to the HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir kodingen som brukes til å skrive parameterne til HTTP-forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: An encoding, as represented by the <xref:System.Text.Encoding> class, defines how to transform characters into a sequence of bytes.
trans-unit.target: Koding, slik det representeres med den <xref:System.Text.Encoding>klasse, definerer hvordan tegn i en sekvens med byte.</xref:System.Text.Encoding>

trans-unit.source: The encoding used to write parameters to the HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Kodingen som brukes til å skrive parametere i HTTP-forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether Web method parameter values are serialized to the out-going HTTP request body.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om parameterverdier for Web-metoden er serialisert til den gamle gå brødteksten i HTTP-forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: The UsesWriteRequest property determines whether the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter.WriteRequest%2A> method is invoked.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen UsesWriteRequest bestemmer om den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter.WriteRequest%2A>metoden aktiveres.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter.WriteRequest%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter> class's implementation of UsesWriteRequest returns a value of `false`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>klassens implementeringen av UsesWriteRequest returnerer en verdi for `false`.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>

trans-unit.source: The only derived class that overrides UsesWriteRequest is <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter>, whose implementation returns a value of `true`.
trans-unit.target: Bare den utledede klassen som overstyrer UsesWriteRequest er <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter>, der implementering returnerer en verdi for `true`.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the Web method parameter values are serialized to the out-going HTTP request body; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis parameterverdier for Web-metoden er serialisert til den gamle gå brødteksten HTTP-forespørselen; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, serializes Web method parameter values into a stream representing the outgoing HTTP request body.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, serializes parameterverdier for Web-metoden til en dataflyt som representerer brødteksten for utgående HTTP-forespørselen.

trans-unit.source: Of the classes derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>, only <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter> implements the WriteRequest method.
trans-unit.target: For klasser som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>, bare <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter>implementerer metoden WriteRequest.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterWriter> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.MimeParameterWriter>

trans-unit.source: An input stream for the outgoing HTTP request's body.
trans-unit.target: En inngående dataflyten for den utgående HTTP-forespørselens meldingsteksten.

trans-unit.source: The Web method parameter values.
trans-unit.target: Parameterverdiene Web-metoden.
